    "id": "article5-death-of-middle-management",
    "titleEn": "The Death of Middle Management: Everyone Becomes a TLM",
    "titleZh": "中层管理的死亡：每个人都要成为 TLM",
    "category": "Opinions",
    "date": "2026-05-30",
    "author": "Sean",
